the agreement six flags texas giant has the highest lift and 
dorneys hercules has the highest drop 
six flags in arlington has been saying its new texas giant is 
143 feet high compared with 95 feet for hercules 
dorney maintained that although the texas ride climbed higher 
hercules plummeted farther because its tracks go over a cliff 
who goes on a roller coaster for the lift said harris 
weinstein chairman of the board of dorney park and wildwater 
kingdom outside allentown 
under the agreement both parks released a statement that said 
in part six flags over texas recognizes that hercules at dorney 
park and wildwater kingdom has the highest drop of any wooden 
roller coaster in the world at 157 feet 
on the other hand dorney park and wildwater kingdom recognize 
that the texas giant at six flags over texas has the highest lift 
of any wooden roller coaster in the world at 143 feet 
michael crowther dorneys director of marketing said the 
general public is perfectly free to develop their own opinion on 
which coaster is the tallest 
a message left for six flags attorney was not returned 
wednesday night 
the agreement was approved by us district judge franklin s 
vanantwerpen 
