following a 65 percent decline in february 
excluding the volatile auto sector sales fell 04 percent in 
march after a strong 15 percent gain a month earlier 
durable goods big ticket items expected to last three or 
more years have been particularly hard hit by interest rates 
because buyers usually borrow to purchase them 
