<TEXT>
with the pomp and circumstance usually 
reserved for state funerals the rich and famous joined in paying 
final respects to ryan white who fought prejudice against aids 
sufferers during his long battle with the disease 
the funeral attended by 1500 people and broadcast live on cnn 
showed how the articulate poised 18yearold had touched the 
nations heart with his pleas for understanding 
first lady barbara bush led the list of dignitaries at the 
