three serving from 1969 to 1977 and from 1985 to 1989 he lost his 
bid for a fourth fouryear term as governor in 1988 to gaston 
caperton 
the silverhaired republican patriarch extended his reign over 
three decades despite a 2to1 registration edge for the democrats 
and almost constant controversy 
