the elections he formed a coalition with the social democrats to 
get the twothirds majority in parliament needed to win 
constitutional changes needed for unification 
the coalition has proven politically expedient as east germans 
first enamored of the idea of quick western prosperity now are 
beginning to fear the loss of their subsidizied homes jobs and 
food 
