pamlico in north carolina said coughlin 67 a former foreign 
correspondent for the los angeles times who was hired as executive 
editor of the daily news a year ago 
it says if you set your standards high enough you can be just 
as good as big town newspapers 
the daily news whose circulation is 10700 won the award for 
breaking town officials long silence about the cancercausing 
chemicals tainting the drinking water the announcement brought 
whoops hollers marching music and champagne into the newsroom of 
