it is a modern urban phenomenon kids robbing 
and sometimes killing other kids over the hottest designer 
sneakers sunglasses or athletic jackets 
in chicago alone four young men have died in little more than a 
year over multicolored satiny jackets with splashy team logos 
across the back 
