shed 18440 points wednesday had opened more than 230 points 
higher before falling 
the dollar edged upward but remained slightly below wednesdays 
levels the us currency closed the morning session at 15837 yen 
up from 15817 yen at the opening but down from 15850 at 
wednesdays finish 
the dollar closed at 15795 yen in new york overnight up from 
15760 yen late tuesday 
estimated volume on the first section of the stock exchange was 
a light 230 million shares 
trading was inactive and investors sold small amounts of 
stock intermittently said kazuyuki suzuki a trader with daiwa 
